text: Bizaardvark is an American comedy television series created by Kyle Stegina and Josh Lehrman. It premiered on Disney Channel on June 24, 2016. The series ran for three seasons. It had a total of 63 episodes. Its final episode was released on April 13, 2019. The series stars Madison Hu, Olivia Rodrigo, Jake Paul, DeVore Ledridge, Ethan Wacker, Maxwell Simkins, and Elie Samouhi. ==References== Category:2010s American comedy television series Category:2016 American television series debuts Category:2019 American television series endings Category:Disney Channel television series Category:English-language television programs Category:Olivia Rodrigo
